2024-03-23 12:55:12.040  INFO 27920 --- [http-nio-8080-exec-4] (84229181755494400) com.example.filter.RequestLogFilter      : 请求处理耗时: 5ms | 响应结果: {"id":84229181755494400,"code":200,"data":[{"id":10,"type":1,"title":"我服了！！","text":"我打打打打打\n\n\n大大大达到\n","images":["http://localhost:8080/images/cache/20240322/2dfc4aac237f41dcbe2cf1a1ec774577"],"time":"2024-03-22T09:12:37.000+00:00","uid":1,"username":"test","avatar":null},{"id":9,"type":1,"title":"开心！！！！考上了陕西理工大学","text":"\n","images":["http://localhost:8080/images/cache/20240322/a4750217cce34e28a5e4f1ba8c06ac70"],"time":"2024-03-22T09:09:20.000+00:00","uid":1,"username":"test","avatar":null},{"id":8,"type":4,"title":"ksl","text":"ksl\n","images":[],"time":"2024-03-22T08:22:22.000+00:00","uid":1,"username":"test","avatar":null},{"id":7,"type":5,"title":"dhsg","text":"qfqfqfqfdsf\n","images":[],"time":"2024-03-22T08:21:00.000+00:00","uid":2,"username":"admin","avatar":"/avatar/c71cb60cc1c04293820fbd439c339fd9"},{"id":6,"type":3,"title":"gsgag","text":"qfqfqfqf\n","images":[],"time":"2024-03-22T08:20:28.000+00:00","uid":2,"username":"admin","avatar":"/avatar/c71cb60cc1c04293820fbd439c339fd9"},{"id":5,"type":3,"title":"qiqniq","text":"wewtaaf\n","images":[],"time":"2024-03-22T08:19:48.000+00:00","uid":2,"username":"admin","avatar":"/avatar/c71cb60cc1c04293820fbd439c339fd9"},{"id":4,"type":4,"title":"fafa","text":"afafaaf\n","images":[],"time":"2024-03-22T08:11:57.000+00:00","uid":2,"username":"admin","avatar":"/avatar/c71cb60cc1c04293820fbd439c339fd9"},{"id":3,"type":1,"title":"adad","text":"在GitHub研究近900个开源AI工具，对了解人工智能生态系统有什么提升？一位人工智能畅销作家和计算机学家帮助全球开发者们做了大量数据分析。一起来看看这份新鲜出炉的开源AI生态报告。\n近期，来自越南的作家和计算机科学家、《设计机器学习系统》作者Chip Huyen（奇普·惠恩）在个人网页发文《我从900个最流行的开源AI工具中学到了什么》，对开源AI工具进行了观察和总结。\n条件限定在Star大于500的仓库，她通过GitHub搜索LLM、GPT和Generative AI等关键词，结果分别为590个、531个和38个。数小时后，她找到了896个仓库，最终获得了845个软件仓库，其中51个是教","images":[],"time":"2024-03-22T07:48:31.000+00:00","uid":2,"username":"admin","avatar":"/avatar/c71cb60cc1c04293820fbd439c339fd9"},{"id":2,"type":1,"title":"嘿嘿","text":"大大大1发额\n","images":[],"time":"2024-03-22T07:16:11.000+00:00","uid":2,"username":"admin","avatar":"/avatar/c71cb60cc1c04293820fbd439c339fd9"},{"id":1,"type":2,"title":"adad","text":"adadadad\n","images":[],"time":"2024-03-21T14:52:53.000+00:00","uid":2,"username":"admin","avatar":"/avatar/c71cb60cc1c04293820fbd439c339fd9"}],"message":"请求成功"}
